Package it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.filters

This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw filters.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AssignFilter This interface models the ASSIGN filter.
ClonesFilter This interface models the CLONES filter.
CopyFilter This interface models a filter which will copy a SemanticDescription into another one.
ExtendsFilter This interface models the EXTENDS filter.
HasFilter This interface models the HAS filter.
HasNotFilter This interface models the HAS-NOT filter.
MatchFilter This interface models the MATCH filter.
OpFilter This interface models an OpFilter, which is a filter which applies an operator to a couple of operands: a property on the left and a list of values on the right.
 

Package it.apice.sapere.api.ecolaws.filters Description

This package contains the definition of SAPERE Ecolaw filters.
